Notas de SQL

*Consultas de informaciòn

Select colum1, colum2 ...
From Table_name
Where condition
  AND/OR other-conditions

--> operadores para las condiciones
*Numeros
los clasicos =, !=, < ...
...Between ... and ...
... Not Between ... and ...
in(number,numer,number)
not in (number, number,...)

*Strings (no olidar que van entre '')
=
like (con la opcion de poner % antes o despues del string si es un fragmento)
not like 
in (...)
not in(...)

***Columna unica!! usa Distinct 

SELECT DISTINCT column, another_column, …
FROM mytable
WHERE condition(s);

***Resultados ordenados
SELECT column, another_column, …
FROM mytable
WHERE condition(s)
ORDER BY column ASC/DESC;

--> ejemplo combinando las dos anteriores:
SELECT Distinct Director FROM movies Order by Director Asc

**Limitando los resultados
SELECT column, another_column, …
FROM mytable
WHERE condition(s)
ORDER BY column ASC/DESC
LIMIT num_limit OFFSET num_offset;

-->Ejemplo: ultimas 4 peliculas de pixar:

SELECT Title FROM movies Order by year Desc Limit 4;

-->Ejemplo la lista de la 6 a la 10ma perlicula de Pixar
SELECT title FROM movies
ORDER BY title ASC
LIMIT 5 OFFSET 5;


